snippet.title: Mosha Gameplay [PC]
snippet.description:
We know everything can be done, if we can imagine it. The World of Mosha is the perfect place to start. We are creators and we want everyone to become a creator. We thrive with passion, this is what we love. Creating videogames & art.

Mosha Online is an online fantasy casual all-in-one RPG tailored for you with love and kawaiiness for Web / Android / PC.

#gamedev #indiedev #indiegame #MoshaOnline

Mosha Online:
https://moshaonline.com

Mosha Go! on Google Play Store:
https://bit.ly/MoshaGo
